title: How the Holy Spirit Led Fr. Jeff from Low-Church Pentecostal to High-Church Anglican
description: This is an except from an interview with Father Jeff Dorn, an Anglican Priest and longtime friend who shared his story on the Tectonic School YouTube channel. The conversation premieres this Monday morning here: https://youtu.be/0XKwQ0_-lng
